Q:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NUVL\" title=\"Nuvalent, Inc.\">NUVL</a></span>) back in September, they were riding serious momentum after some important updates at the ESMO congress. That momentum was coupled to a large cash raise that eliminates</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811852453/image_1811852453.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742791-nuvalent-steps-toward-that-favorable-entry-point", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 13:15:22"}, {"id": "4742790", "title": "Deramiocel's Promise Brightens Capricor's Outlook, With Strings Attached", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Individuals Joining Together As Team, Company, Family or Network.\" data-id=\"170042080\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JamesBrey</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Capricor Therapeutics Targets DMD Cardiomyopathy With Deramiocel</h2> <p><strong>Capricor Therapeutics</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CAPR\" title=\"Capricor Therapeutics, Inc.\">CAPR</a></span>) is advancing deramiocel, an allogeneic cell therapy, for DMD-related cardiomyopathy. The company initiated a rolling BLA submission in October, with a decision expected in the second half of 2025. Deramiocel had</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170042080/image_170042080.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742790-deramiocels-promise-brightens-capricors-outlook-with-strings-attached", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 13:08:41"}, {"id": "4742789", "title": "TD Bank: Massive Overreaction (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"TD Bank Branch\" data-id=\"1738185835\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/image_1738185835.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738185835/ima