hat\u2019s driving this rally is the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157192339/image_157192339.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742782-nlr-promising-and-still-has-an-attractive-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:15:55"}, {"id": "4742781", "title": "Richmond Mutual Bancorporation: Risk-Return Profile Not Attractive For Long-Term Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female hand inserting bank card into automatic cash machine (ATM) to access bank account services in the city\" data-id=\"1977075709\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming 